        </div>
      </aside>

      <main class="about-main">
        <section class="bio-section">
          <h2>Background</h2>
          <p>
            I'm a technology leader with over [X] years of experience building and scaling
            engineering teams at companies ranging from startups to Fortune 500 enterprises.
          </p>
          <p>
            Currently, I [describe your current role/position]. Previously, I held leadership
            positions at [previous companies], where I [key accomplishments].
          </p>
          <p>
            My passion lies at the intersection of technology and business strategy. I believe
            that the best technical solutions are ones that directly address real business needs
            and create measurable value.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="bio-section">
          <h2>What I Focus On</h2>
          <ul class="focus-list">
            <li>
              <strong>Engineering Leadership</strong> - Building high-performing teams through
              mentorship, clear communication, and creating environments where people can do
              their best work.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Technical Strategy</strong> - Aligning technology investments with
              business objectives to maximize ROI and competitive advantage.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Digital Transformation</strong> - Helping organizations modernize their
              technology stack and processes to stay competitive.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Knowledge Sharing</strong> - Speaking at conferences and writing about
              lessons learned in technology leadership.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="bio-section">
          <h2>Beyond Work</h2>
          <p>
            When I'm not working, you'll find me [your hobbies/interests]. I'm also an avid
            reader, and you can see what I've been reading on my <a href="/books">Books</a> page.
          </p>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 250px 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .about-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(60px + var(--spacing-lg));
    align-self: start;
  }

  .profile-image {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .image-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 2px dashed var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .social-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .social-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .about-main {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .bio-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .bio-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .bio-section p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .bio-section a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .focus-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .focus-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .focus-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6rem;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .focus-list strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-sidebar {
      position: static;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .profile-image {
      width: 200px;
    }

    .social-links {
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
